      "description": "Presenting a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity during high-G cornering. The M Variable Differential Lock provides exceptional mechanical grip, while the factory-tuned suspension offers a precise, communicative chassis response. Showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are sharp and the high-revving 8,000 RPM redline remains as intoxicating as ever. An analog icon ready for the backroads.",
